data: Consider the average difference between K-12 enrollment and 15-17 enrollment of schools that are locally funded, list the names and DOC type of schools which has a difference above this average.
AI Generated SQL Query

```WITH avg_diff AS (  SELECT AVG(`Enrollment (K-12)` - `Enrollment (Ages 5-17)`) AS avg_diff  FROM frpm  WHERE `FundingType` = 'Locally Funded')SELECT s.`School`, s.`DOCType`FROM frpm fJOIN schools s ON f.`CDSCode` = s.`CDSCode`WHERE f.`FundingType` = 'Locally Funded'AND f.`Enrollment (K-12)` - f.`Enrollment (Ages 5-17)` > (SELECT avg_diff FROM avg_diff);```

Consider the average difference between K-12 enrollment and 15-17 enrollment of schools that are locally funded, list the names and DOC type of schools which has a difference above this average.
Gold Standard SQL Query

SELECT T2.School, T2.DOC FROM frpm AS T1 INNER JOIN schools AS T2 ON T1.CDSCode = T2.CDSCode WHERE T2.FundingType = 'Locally funded' AND (T1.`Enrollment (K-12)` - T1.`Enrollment (Ages 5-17)`) > (SELECT AVG(T3.`Enrollment (K-12)` - T3.`Enrollment (Ages 5-17)`) FROM frpm AS T3 INNER JOIN schools AS T4 ON T3.CDSCode = T4.CDSCode WHERE T4.FundingType = 'Locally funded')
What was the growth rate of the total amount of loans across all accounts for a male client between 1996 and 1997?
AI Generated SQL Query

```WITH male_loans_1996 AS (  SELECT SUM(amount) AS total_amount_1996  FROM loan  JOIN account ON loan.account_id = account.account_id  JOIN client ON account.district_id = client.district_id  WHERE client.gender = 'M' AND loan.date BETWEEN '1996-01-01' AND '1996-12-31'),male_loans_1997 AS (  SELECT SUM(amount) AS total_amount_1997  FROM loan  JOIN account ON loan.account_id = account.account_id  JOIN client ON account.district_id = client.district_id  WHERE client.gender = 'M' AND loan.date BETWEEN '1997-01-01' AND '1997-12-31')SELECT (male_loans_1997.total_amount_1997 - male_loans_1996.total_amount_1996) / male_loans_1996.total_amount_1996 * 100 AS growth_rateFROM male_loans_1996, male_loans_1997;```
Incorrect
What was the growth rate of the total amount of loans across all accounts for a male client between 1996 and 1997?
Gold Standard SQL Query

SELECT CAST((SUM(CASE WHEN STRFTIME('%Y', T1.date) = '1997' THEN T1.amount ELSE 0 END) - SUM(CASE WHEN STRFTIME('%Y', T1.date) = '1996' THEN T1.amount ELSE 0 END)) AS REAL) * 100 / SUM(CASE WHEN STRFTIME('%Y', T1.date) = '1996' THEN T1.amount ELSE 0 END) FROM loan AS T1 INNER JOIN account AS T2 ON T1.account_id = T2.account_id INNER JOIN disp AS T3 ON T3.account_id = T2.account_id INNER JOIN client AS T4 ON T4.client_id = T3.client_id WHERE T4.gender = 'M' AND T3.type = 'OWNER'
What are the elements of the toxicology and label of molecule TR060?
AI Generated SQL Query

Correct
What are the elements of the toxicology and label of molecule TR060?
Gold Standard SQL Query
SELECT DISTINCT T1.element, T2.label FROM atom AS T1 INNER JOIN molecule AS T2 ON T1.molecule_id = T2.molecule_id WHERE T2.molecule_id = 'TR060'
